Lee/md/01\" alt=\"\">\n</p><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><ol class=\"linenums\"><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\">//自底向上的归并排序(非递归)</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"kwd\">public</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">static</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">void</span><span class=\"pln\"> sort2</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">[]</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">){</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> n </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> arr</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">length</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    aux </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">new</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pun\">[</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">length</span><span class=\"pun\">];</span><span class=\"com\">//初始化临时数组</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"com\">//不同的子数组size 1 --&gt;2--&gt;4。。。。</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"kwd\">for</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> sz </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"lit\">1</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\">sz</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;</span><span class=\"pln\">n</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\">sz</span><span class=\"pun\">+=</span><span class=\"pln\">sz</span><span class=\"pun\">){</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">        </span><span class=\"kwd\">for</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> lo </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"lit\">0</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\">lo</span><span class=\"pun\">&lt;</span><span class=\"pln\">n</span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"pln\">sz</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span><span class=\"pln\">lo</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\">lo</span><span class=\"pun\">+</span><span class=\"lit\">2</span><span class=\"pun\">*</span><span class=\"pln\">sz</span><span class=\"pun\">){</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">            </span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> mid </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> lo</span><span class=\"pun\">+</span><span class=\"pln\">sz</span><span class=\"pun\">/</span><span class=\"lit\">2</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">            merge</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> lo</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> mid</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"typ\">Math</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">min</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">lo</span><span class=\"pun\">+</span><span class=\"pln\">sz</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> n</span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"lit\">1</span><span class=\"pun\">));</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">        </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pun\">}</span></code></li></ol></pre>\n<h3 id=\"h3-u5206u6790u603Bu7ED3\"><a name=\"分析总结\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>分析总结</h3><p>​    归并排序时间复杂度无论是在最好情况下还是在最坏情况下均是O(nlog2n)。是一种稳定的排序算法，但是在空间复杂度(O(n))上不是最优的，因为它要借助一个辅助数组。</p>\n','Jann Lee',NULL,2,'201803270927_434.jpg?imageView1/JannLee/md/01',12,2,0,0,0,'2018-03-28 19:58:23','2018-04-02 01:42:12'),(147,1,'排序算法---快速排序','### 概述\n\n 	快速排序是当前应用最广泛的算法，由于其实现简单且效率高，使用与各种输入模型且在一般应用中比其他排序算法要快。它最大的特色就是`原地排序`，并且将长度为n的数组排序所需要的时间与nlgn成正比。快速排序的内循环比大多数排序...','<h3 id=\"h3-u6982u8FF0\"><a name=\"概述\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>概述</h3><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><ol class=\"linenums\"><li class=\"L0\"><code><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">快速排序是当前应用最广泛的算法，由于其实现简单且效率高，使用与各种输入模型且在一般应用中比其他排序算法要快。它最大的特色就是</span><span class=\"str\">`原地排序`</span><span class=\"pun\">，并且将长度为</span><span class=\"pln\">n</span><span class=\"pun\">的数组排序所需要的时间与</span><span class=\"pln\">nlgn</span><span class=\"pun\">成正比。快速排序的内循环比大多数排序算法要小，所以无论在理论上还是实际上都要更快。</span></code></li></ol></pre><p>​    <u>基本原理</u> :与归并排序是互补的，快速排序是将数组切分为两个子数组，然后对子数组进行排序，当子数组都有序时排序就完成了。</p>\n<p>​    切分：切分是快速排序中的核心部分，即随机选取一个元素作为<code>切分元素</code>，然后从数组的左端 向右扫描直到找到一个大于等于它的元素，再从右端向左端扫描找到一个小于等于它的元素，然后交换他们的位置。如此继续，直到左右指针相遇时，我们只需要将切分元素与左子数组和左子数组最右侧元素交换并返回最右侧元素下标即可。</p>\n<h3 id=\"h3--\"><a name=\"一、切分\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>一、切分</h3><h4 id=\"h4-u5207u5206u8F68u8FF9u56FE\"><a name=\"切分轨迹图\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>切分轨迹图</h4><p><img src=\"http://p34qzbztu.bkt.clouddn.com/201803300856_6.png?imageView1/JannLee/md/01\" alt=\"\">\n</p><h4 id=\"h4-u4EE3u7801u5B9Eu73B0\"><a name=\"代码实现\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>代码实现</h4><p>public static void exch(int [] arr ,int i,int j ){</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><ol class=\"linenums\"><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\">//交换数组中元素位置</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"kwd\">public</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">static</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">void</span><span class=\"pln\"> exch</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">[]</span><span class=\"pln\"> arr </span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> i</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> j </span><span class=\"pun\">){</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> temp </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> arr</span><span class=\"pun\">[</span><span class=\"pln\">i</span><span class=\"pun\">];</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    arr</span><span class=\"pun\">[</span><span class=\"pln\">i</span><span class=\"pun\">]=</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">[</span><span class=\"pln\">j</span><span class=\"pun\">];</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    arr</span><span class=\"pun\">[</span><span class=\"pln\">j</span><span class=\"pun\">]=</span><span class=\"pln\">temp</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pun\">}</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\">//切分</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"kwd\">public</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">static</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> partition</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">[]</span><span class=\"pln\"> arr</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> lo</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> hi</span><span class=\"pun\">){</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"com\">//左右指针，初始位置未指向需要比较的元素</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> i </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> lo</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> j </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> hi</span><span class=\"pun\">+</span><span class=\"lit\">1</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"com\">//切分元素</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> flag </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> arr</span><span class=\"pun\">[</span><span class=\"pln\">lo</span><span class=\"pun\">];</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"kwd\">while</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"kwd\">true</span><span class=\"pun\">){</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">        </span><span class=\"com\">//指针未到达边界，且左指针指向的小于flag，右指针指向的大于flag移动指针</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">        </span><span class=\"kwd\">while</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">[++</span><span class=\"pln\">i</span><span class=\"pun\">]&lt;</span><span class=\"pln\">flag</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">i</span><span class=\"pun\">==</span><span class=\"pln\">hi</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">break</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">        </span><span class=\"kwd\">while</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">[++</span><span class=\"pln\">j</span><span class=\"pun\">]&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">flag</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">j</span><span class=\"pun\">==</span><span class=\"pln\">lo</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">break</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">        </span><span class=\"com\">//如果左指针和右指针相遇,跳出循环，否则交换左右指针位置元素</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">        </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">i</span><span class=\"pun\">&gt;=</span><span class=\"pln\">j</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">break</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">        exch</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\">i</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\">j</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"pun\">}</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"com\">//交换切分元素与左子数组最右边元素</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    exch</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\">lo</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\">j</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">      </span><span class=\"kwd\">return</span><span class=\"pln\"> j</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pun\">}</span></code></li></ol></pre>\n<h3 id=\"h3--\"><a name=\"二、排序\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>二、排序</h3><h4 id=\"h4-u5FEBu901Fu6392u5E8Fu793Au610Fu56FE\"><a name=\"快速排序示意图\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>快速排序示意图</h4><p><img src=\"http://p34qzbztu.bkt.clouddn.com/201803300913_661.png?imageView1/JannLee/md/01\" alt=\"\">\n</p><h4 id=\"h4-u4EE3u7801u5B9Eu73B0\"><a name=\"代码实现\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>代码实现</h4><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><ol class=\"linenums\"><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"kwd\">public</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">static</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">void</span><span class=\"pln\"> sort</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">[]</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> lo</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> hi</span><span class=\"pun\">){</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"kwd\">if</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">lo</span><span class=\"pun\">&gt;=</span><span class=\"pln\">hi</span><span class=\"pun\">)</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">return</span><span class=\"pun\">;</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">      </span><span class=\"com\">//对数组进行拆分</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"kwd\">int</span><span class=\"pln\"> j </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> partition</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> lo</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> hi</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">      </span><span class=\"com\">//最左右子数组进行排序</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    sort</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> lo</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> j</span><span class=\"pun\">-</span><span class=\"lit\">1</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">    sort</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"pln\">arr</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\">j</span><span class=\"pun\">+</span><span class=\"lit\">1</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\">hi</span><span class=\"pun\">);</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pun\">}</span></code></li></ol></pre>\n<p>三、总结</p>\n<p>​    快速排序切分的内循环会用一个递增索引将数组元素和一个定制值比较。这种简洁也是快速排序的一个优点，很难想象出比这种更短小的内循环的排序算法了。例如，归并排序和希尔排序一般都比快速排序慢，原因就是他们还在内循环中移动数据。</p>\n','Jann Lee',NULL,2,'201803300856_6.png?imageView1/JannLee/md/01',9,2,0,0,0,'2018-03-30 09:26:33','2018-04-02 01:41:39'),(148,7,'JDK源码解析---HashMap&HashTable','### 一、HashMap源码注解\n\n```java\n/*\n * Hash table based implementation of the <tt>Map</tt> interface.  This\n * implementation ...','<h3 id=\"h3--hashmap-\"><a name=\"一、HashMap源码注解\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>一、HashMap源码注解</h3><pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><ol class=\"linenums\"><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\">/*</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * Hash table based implementation of the &lt;tt&gt;Map&lt;/tt&gt; interface.  This</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * implementation provides all of the optional map operations, and permits</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;tt&gt;null&lt;/tt&gt; values and the &lt;tt&gt;null&lt;/tt&gt; key.  (The &lt;tt&gt;HashMap&lt;/tt&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * class is roughly equivalent to &lt;tt&gt;Hashtable&lt;/tt&gt;, except that it is</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * unsynchronized and permits nulls.)  This class makes no guarantees as to</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * the order of the map; in particular, it does not guarantee that the order</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * will remain constant over time.</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> *</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;p&gt;This implementation provides constant-time performance for the basic</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * operations (&lt;tt&gt;get&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;put&lt;/tt&gt;), assuming the hash function</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * disperses the elements properly among the buckets.  Iteration over</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * collection views requires time proportional to the \"capacity\" of the</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;tt&gt;HashMap&lt;/tt&gt; instance (the number of buckets) plus its size (the number</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * of key-value mappings).  Thus, it\'s very important not to set the initial</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * capacity too high (or the load factor too low) if iteration performance is</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * important.</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> *</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;p&gt;An instance of &lt;tt&gt;HashMap&lt;/tt&gt; has two parameters that affect its</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * performance: &lt;i&gt;initial capacity&lt;/i&gt; and &lt;i&gt;load factor&lt;/i&gt;.  The</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;i&gt;capacity&lt;/i&gt; is the number of buckets in the hash table, and the initial</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * capacity is simply the capacity at the time the hash table is created.  The</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;i&gt;load factor&lt;/i&gt; is a measure of how full the hash table is allowed to</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * get before its capacity is automatically increased.  When the number of</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * entries in the hash table exceeds the product of the load factor and the</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * current capacity, the hash table is &lt;i&gt;rehashed&lt;/i&gt; (that is, internal data</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * structures are rebuilt) so that the hash table has approximately twice the</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * number of buckets.</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> *</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;p&gt;As a general rule, the default load factor (.75) offers a good tradeoff</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * between time and space costs.  Higher values decrease the space overhead</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * but increase the lookup cost (reflected in most of the operations of the</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;tt&gt;HashMap&lt;/tt&gt; class, including &lt;tt&gt;get&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;put&lt;/tt&gt;).  The</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * expected number of entries in the map and its load factor should be taken</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * into account when setting its initial capacity, so as to minimize the</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * number of rehash operations.  If the initial capacity is greater</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * than the maximum number of entries divided by the load factor, no</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * rehash operations will ever occur.</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> *</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;p&gt;If many mappings are to be stored in a &lt;tt&gt;HashMap&lt;/tt&gt; instance,</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * creating it with a sufficiently large capacity will allow the mappings to</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * be stored more efficiently than letting it perform automatic rehashing as</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * needed to grow the table.</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> *</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note that this implementation is not synchronized.&lt;/strong&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * If multiple threads access a hash map concurrently, and at least one of</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * the threads modifies the map structurally, it &lt;i&gt;must&lt;/i&gt; be</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * synchronized externally.  (A structural modification is any operation</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * that adds or deletes one or more mappings; merely changing the value</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * associated with a key that an instance already contains is not a</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * structural modification.)  This is typically accomplished by</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * synchronizing on some object that naturally encapsulates the map.</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> *</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * If no such object exists, the map should be \"wrapped\" using the</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * {@link Collections#synchronizedMap Collections.synchronizedMap}</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * method.  This is best done at creation time, to prevent accidental</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * unsynchronized access to the map:&lt;pre&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> *   Map m = Collections.synchronizedMap(new HashMap(...));&lt;/pre&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> *</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;p&gt;The iterators returned by all of this class\'s \"collection view methods\"</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * are &lt;i&gt;fail-fast&lt;/i&gt;: if the map is structurally modified at any time after</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * the iterator is created, in any way except through the iterator\'s own</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;tt&gt;remove&lt;/tt&gt; method, the iterator will throw a</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * {@link ConcurrentModificationException}.  Thus, in the face of concurrent</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * modification, the iterator fails quickly and cleanly, rather than risking</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * arbitrary, non-deterministic behavior at an undetermined time in the</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * future.</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> *</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * &lt;p&gt;Note that the fail-fast behavior of an iterator cannot be guaranteed</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * as it is, generally speaking, impossible to make any hard guarantees in the</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * presence of unsynchronized concurrent modification.  Fail-fast iterators</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * throw &lt;tt&gt;ConcurrentModificationException&lt;/tt&gt; on a best-effort basis.</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * Therefore, it would be wrong to write a program that depended on this</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * exception for its correctness: &lt;i&gt;the fail-fast behavior of iterators</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> * should be used only to detect bugs.&lt;/i&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"com\"> */</span></code></li></ol></pre>\n<h4 id=\"h4-u80E1u4E71u7FFBu8BD1u7684\"><a name=\"胡乱翻译的\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>胡乱翻译的</h4><p>Hash table基于Map接口的实现，这个实现提供了所有可选择的操作，并且允许null value和null  key。(HashMap大致上与HashTable相等，除了没有同步和允许null的键或值),这个类不保证map中键值对的顺序，特别是随着时间的推移保证map的顺序。</p>\n<p>假设hash方法能在hash桶中适当分散元素，这个实现为基本get和put操作提供了常量时间的性能。迭代集合视图需要的时间与容量成正比，即hashmap实例hash桶的数量，增加hasp中keyvalue的数量的大小。所以，如果迭代性能很重要的话，一定不要给初始容量设置的太大(或者加载因素太低)。</p>\n<p>影响HashMap性能的因素有两个：初始容量和负荷系数(扩容的条件)。容量就是hash桶在hash表中的数量，初始容量只是在hash表被创建时的容量。负荷系数是一个测量在hash表在那种程度下在获取元素之前自动进行扩容。当键值对数量超过负荷银子和当前容量，hash 表会被rehash（内部数据结构重构），以至于hash表有大约两倍桶的数量。</p>\n<p>作为一般规则，默认的负载系数(.75)提供了一个很好的权衡。在时间和空间成本之间。更高的值会减少空间开销。但是增加查找成本(反映在HashMap类大多数操作中，包括get和put) . map理想数量的键值对和负荷系数在初始化容量时应该被考虑在内，为了最小化rehash操作的数量。<code>如果初始容量比负荷因数划分的最大数量键值对还要大，rehash将永远不会发生</code>。</p>\n<p>如果很多映射被存入hashmap对象，并且以足够的容量来存储映射。这样将比让它自动rehash来增加hashtable容量更加高效。</p>\n<p><em>注意</em>这个实现是不同步的，如果多线程同时访问hashmap，并且至少有一个修改map的结构（执行put或delete操作或key-value中的值发生改变），必须在外部进行同步。这通常是通过在一些对象上同步实现的，这些对象自然地封装了map.如果没有这种对象，这个map应该在创建的时候使用Collections.synchronizedMap进行装饰(同步)。为了防止意外访问没有同步的map，最好在创建之初进行装饰。</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><ol class=\"linenums\"><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-java\"><span class=\"pln\">  </span><span class=\"typ\">Map</span><span class=\"pln\"> m </span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"typ\">Collections</span><span class=\"pun\">.</span><span class=\"pln\">synchronizedMap</span><span class=\"pun\">(</span><span class=\"kwd\">new</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"typ\">HashMap</span><span class=\"pun\">(...));</span></code></li></ol></pre>\n<p>类的集合视图方法返回的迭代器是fail-fast。如果map在迭代期被创建之后被结构性地修改，除了迭代期使用自己的remove方法，否则都会抛出一个</p>\n<p>ConcurrentModificationException异常。因此，在并发修改的情况下，迭代期快速果断的报错而不是在未来的时间里无征兆的报错。</p>\n<p>注意迭代器的fast-fail是不能保证的，通常来说，在不同步的并发修改情况下。Fail-fast 迭代器会尽可能的抛出ConcurrentModificationException 。因此，编写一个依赖fast-fail机制的程序是错误的，正确的做法是它仅仅用于错误的检测。</p>\n<h3 id=\"h3--\"><a name=\"二、概念解释\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>二、概念解释</h3><p><code>load factor</code>:负载因子，决定扩容阀值，当size&gt;load factor*capacity时进行扩容</p>\n<p><code>size</code>:HashMap中存放键值对数量</p>\n<p><code>capacity</code>:容量，当前可容纳的键值对数量最大值，默认值为16，每次扩容都是capacity&lt;&lt;1（乘以2）</p>\n<h3 id=\"h3--\"><a name=\"三、 常用方法\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>三、 常用方法</h3><p>put方法</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><o